"{\"uid\": \"prevention.com-health-a61635886-olympic-gymnast-aly-raisman-hospitalized-stroke-like-symptoms\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was so scary,\\\" the Olympic gymnast said.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 44, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We may earn commission from links on this page, but we only recommend products we back.Why Trust Us?\", \"from\": 46, \"to\": 146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since her retirement, Olympic gymnastAly Raismanhas been hospitalized twice for\\\"stroke-like symptoms,\\\"she recently told Alex Cooper on theCall Her Daddypodcast.\", \"from\": 148, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\", \"score\": 0.8607573575018954, \"rank\": 0.16176470588237404, \"text\": \"Alex Cooper\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the interview, Raisman recounted the experiences and attributed them both to trauma and stress.\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you do not pick a day to rest, your body will pick it for you,\\\"-that quote, Raisman said,  \\\"encapsulates\\\" her episodes.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a baseline, she tends to have \\\"different minor issues\\\" with her health \\\"depending on what I am going through at the time,\\\" she said, but there were two \\\"intense\\\" events during which she was reviewed for stroke-like symptoms.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not remember my name.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am slurring my words.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can barely speak.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both times I was tested for a stroke because I literally could not move my body,\\\" she recalled.\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are not familiar, the symptoms of astroke, according to theNational Heart, Blood, and Lung Institute, are:  Raisman said it was all \\\"so scary,\\\" a fear that was exacerbated by the PTSD she lives with as a result of the abuse she experienced in medical settings as a young gymnast.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2018, U.S. gymnastics doctor Larry Nassarwas sentenced to up to 175 years in prisonfor sexually abusing his patients, among other sex crimes.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over 150 women, including Raisman, came forward as victims.\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raisman's past made her understandably wary when it came to being alone with medics during her recent health scares.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first time it happened was during COVID.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so, they would not let my mom in the ambulance with me,\\\" she recalled.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was aware enough to know, 'Oh my God, I have two men [with me], I can not move my arms and my legs, I can not move my body, I can not speak.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What if they take advantage of me?'\\\"\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was really still struggling a lot with PTSD,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People do not realize how much it still lives with you when you have been through something traumatic.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, that was really hard for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The second episode happened a year and a half later, Raisman explained, and struck her with \\\"complete body paralysis\\\" that left her hospitalized for three days.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They would not release me because I could not sit up on my own.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me so long.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I needed help walking, going to the bathroom,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the most [difficult] to be able to go from being an athlete and being able to push myself so much to literally not even be able to move my fingers, move my legs.\\\"\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the medical community, bouts of stroke-like symptoms are known as \\\"stroke mimics,\\\"  and they have been linked to a series of potential causes including migraines, vertigo, and, commonly, functional neurological disorder (FND), per theAmerican Heart Association (AHA), which is a condition that can affect sensation, movement, speech, and vision.\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2747, \"end\": 2750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Functional_neurologic_disorder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FND\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Functional_neurologic_disorder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Functional_neurologic_disorder\"}, {\"begin\": 2788, \"end\": 2791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Heart_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.75758428581487e-20, \"text\": \"AHA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Heart_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Heart_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PTSD symptomsare commonin people with FNDs, and researchers think PTSD could even be a cause of them.\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A recentstudyfound that people who have stroke mimics are susceptible to developing (or developing worsened) PTSD.\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 3088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wonder what is the chicken and what is the egg here?\\\"\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Natalia Rost, M.D., chief of the stroke division at Massachusetts General Hospital in Boston told the AHA.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3147, \"end\": 3154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natalia_Pushkina\", \"score\": 0.9790369278161798, \"rank\": 0.021411932060921478, \"text\": \"Natalia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natalia_Pushkina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natalia_Pushkina\"}, {\"begin\": 3161, \"end\": 3165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physician\", \"score\": 0.9999997802006206, \"rank\": 2.1979950027876985e-07, \"text\": \"M.D.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physician\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physician\"}, {\"begin\": 3199, \"end\": 3229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts_General_Hospital\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Massachusetts General Hospital\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts_General_Hospital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts_General_Hospital\"}, {\"begin\": 3233, \"end\": 3239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"score\": 0.9999999831447896, \"rank\": 1.685347422478075e-08, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\"}, {\"begin\": 3249, \"end\": 3252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Heart_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.75758428581487e-20, \"text\": \"AHA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Heart_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Heart_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Folks who are vulnerable to psychological stress can experience stroke mimics, which could be the strongest connection to developing PTSD after a stroke mimic.\\\"\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With so much unknown about stroke mimics, Raisman said she was initially \\\"ignored\\\" by doctors.\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's appalling,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It wasn't until they realized that I was a very high-level athlete, that they were very nice to me and taking care of me, which is also triggering for me because I already have trust issues with doctors.\\\"\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3745, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sinceher retirement from gymnastics in 2020, she has been focusing on her personal life.\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been doing therapy for many years, and I think therapy can be so impactful and so helpful,\\\" she toldWondermindin 2022.\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really just trying to remember that it's important for me to just stick with it, be patient, communicate with my therapist, my friends, and family.\", \"from\": 3963, \"to\": 4116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am just kind of taking it day by day.\\\"\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the upcoming Paris Summer Games, Raisman will be an official hospitality ambassador alongside Michael Phelps, perNBC, and she's curious to see how her body will react.\", \"from\": 4162, \"to\": 4336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4263, \"end\": 4277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4806870888289e-26, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am gonna be so busy,\\\" she told Cooper.\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is gonna be a lot of triggers.\", \"from\": 4379, \"to\": 4416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I might see someone that maybe did not protect me in the past.\", \"from\": 4417, \"to\": 4479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, it's working on that.\", \"from\": 4480, \"to\": 4505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very complicated.\\\"\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"16 Skin Spots You Should Get Checked Out Promptly  Dave Coulier Reveals New Cancer Diagnosis  How I Personalized My Severe Asthma Management  FDA: 1.5 Million Bags of Shredded Cheese Recalled  Norovirus Vs.\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4673, \"end\": 4676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.604144943156573e-50, \"text\": \"FDA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flu: How to Tell Which You Have  Should You Take Ashwagandha or Magnesium to Sleep?\", \"from\": 4738, \"to\": 4821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4787, \"end\": 4798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Withania_somnifera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ashwagandha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Withania_somnifera\", \"dbpedia\": \"